{"tid":1127830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"農民插秧忽遭閃電擊中　瞬間倒地亡","createTime":"2019-04-27T11:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T01:20:54.000Z","uid":118120,"like":111,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"1681193bc87c0df3b84446a40a26b12c8ebfcdf5","tid":1127830,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427045129930-0427_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190427050309\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427045129930-0427_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190427050309&h=49e96ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天有不測風雲，人有旦夕禍福。江西吉安市泰和縣一名農民，周三（24日）在田裏插秧時，忽被雷電擊中，隨即倒在田裏。知情人士透露，該名農民當場死亡。目前，當局仍就具體情況進行調查。 <br />\n<br />\n從網傳短片可見，當時天色較暗，但未見風雨，現場地勢亦較平坦，附近未有大樹或建築物。本來該農民正彎腰插秧，惟忽然一道白光擊中他身處的位置，只見他站直身子不到一秒，便倒在田裏，附近村民亦未有反應。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tnrbxeVuUuk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtnrbxeVuUuk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=6fbecca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tnrbxeVuUuk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"0f94d47793465bd98d050601d9c2b3d2bf286ad6","tid":1127830,"uid":162866,"like":5,"dislike":91,"score":-86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"連登返風向指標：<br />\n今次連登仔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1497abdb15dfb88c63cde1d70fad7cd657faca9","tid":1127830,"uid":78873,"like":396,"dislike":5,"score":391,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9138c1880a9cadb76d50053ea3630e50425959","tid":1127830,"uid":3818,"like":123,"dislike":5,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T11:30:03.000Z","msg":"中共試緊新武器<img src=\"/assets/face